name: Hypocrite
description:
We're human, we have some bad habits


Hypocrite. Situation where are humans said something that doesn't match with the action. It can be anything; feelings, words, and thoughts. But, strangely we always believe in this creature and get hurt with that. Honestly, we are knowing about that human habits but sometimes, we just again and again to believe in this creature. And that's we are, a human. 


The
most
unpredictable

in this world.


We just have a one face, but we have some various mask to use it.
